{"tid":1625504,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"[良心］KAWS 爭議作品《MAO》於香港 Sotheby's 拍賣會緊急下架","createTime":"2019-10-05T07:10:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T14:16:59.000Z","uid":136342,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9b29aaad65d6122724ae42f9ca2b474ca7aff4b5","tid":1625504,"uid":136342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:10:23.000Z","msg":"該作品引起廣大中國網民的批評，在 KAWS 的個人社群帳號上留下了無數則負面言論與焚燒 KAWS 作品的影片。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n還記得上月底為各位介紹 Sotheby&rsquo;s 拍賣行即將在香港和紐約等地舉辦拍賣會，其中將會出現多件 KAWS 的罕見作品，然而就在上週公佈部分拍賣清單時，於 Sotheby&rsquo;s 官方網站上出現了一件名為「UNTITLED」的畫作，其主題十分明顯的是以前任中華人民共和國主席毛澤東作為主角，並將其加上 KAWS 經典的設計元素，包括「XX」眼睛、骷髏和骨頭。該作品原預計將以 $79,000 至 $121,000 美元售出，但現在已正式下架，不會開放競標。<br />\n<br />\n對此，KAWS 受到廣大網民的撻伐，他們認為該作品和 KAWS 本人污辱了中國和中國人民，KAWS 的個人社群帳戶包括微博、Instagram 等等皆迅速被負面留言填滿，網路上也流傳出許多憤怒民眾焚燒 KAWS 作品的影片，而 UNIQLO China 和再售平台 Poizon 也隨即下架與 KAWS 有關的所有服飾。<br />\n<br />\nKAWS 本人稍早緊急地在個人 Instagram 上發表聲明：「我永遠不會創作侵犯他人、團體或國家的作品，我一直都以熱門的題材為主題，如同我在 2001 年完成的這件作品。這件作品（指《MAO》）沒有任何政治動機，也不應該再現在被作為一種政治武器。我的家人、朋友和粉絲來自世界各地，他們知道我對創作的熱愛和對所有人的尊敬。」<br />\n<br />\n燒Vans, 買Kaws!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e42f90ab7a643fa182b79d0e8b60aef91654c43","tid":1625504,"uid":136342,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:11:11.000Z","msg":"凡是敵人反對的 我們就要擁護<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dc7f9c91515a7c563c02bb9ea385348908c72f4","tid":1625504,"uid":136342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:11:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e8b0be403a3dc38d5066ff767e7ccfcac1bbc563","tid":1625504,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:12:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bcd1b8725eec1e57d07663561a572abc5fdde977","tid":1625504,"uid":266231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:12:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"25365c68aca139b4339a427e776464e301818d45","tid":1625504,"uid":136342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bcd1b8725eec1e57d07663561a572abc5fdde977","tid":1625504,"uid":266231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:12:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:13:56.000Z","msg":"我哋呢啲一般市民<br />\n就算冇下架都冇可能買到佢幅畫<br />\n但係你可以支持下其他藝術品<br />\n或者佢啲衫褲"},{"pid":"b2ba6d906178f6ceae255d6a320874be13c3e5e1","tid":1625504,"uid":161848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:21:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撐你老母咩，跪低咗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"ab871fab906dfda3fbfb27a04bcc28904e74eb49","tid":1625504,"uid":123587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:15:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/news_res/2019/10/01/261449/i_494x397_015195055.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Fnews_res%2F2019%2F10%2F01%2F261449%2Fi_494x397_015195055.jpg&h=91f03de2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7ffb77c0974a4835cc8d125fd23cf685e977c0e2","tid":1625504,"uid":136342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2ba6d906178f6ceae255d6a320874be13c3e5e1","tid":1625504,"uid":161848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:21:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撐你老母咩，跪低咗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:16:28.000Z","msg":"係？"},{"pid":"2ea4fb5627a0ed90078f699a64d23808044cd9e3","tid":1625504,"uid":123587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bcd1b8725eec1e57d07663561a572abc5fdde977","tid":1625504